ke%20in%20the%20military.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20if%20they%20had%20seen%20the%20shooting%20suspect%20more%20quickly%2C%20counter-snipers%20may%20not%20always%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20act%20immediately%20when%20they%20spot%20a%20threat%2C%20according%20to%20Anthony%20Cangelosi%2C%20a%20former%20special%20agent%20who%20directed%20the%20Secret%20Service's%20technical%20security%20advances%20for%20presidential%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20either%20have%20to%20make%20a%20decision%3A%20'Do%20I%20take%20a%20shot%3F%20Or%20do%20I%20not%20take%20a%20shot%3F'%26quot%3B%20Cangelosi%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20you%20find%20out%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20just%20killed%20a%2020-year-old%20kid%20who%20loves%20the%20protectee%2C%20and%20he%20couldn't%20get%20in%20the%20venue%2C%20and%20he%20just%20wanted%20to%20get%20up%20on%20that%20roof%3F'%20No%20one%20wants%20to%20be%20in%20that%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20Cangelosi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECangelosi%20said%20the%20Secret%20Service%20team%20at%20the%20event%20should%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bsite%20plan%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20include%20a%20layout%20of%20the%20area%20and%20the%20surrounding%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20scene%20of%20the%20Trump%20assassination%20attempt%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20shows%20empty%20bleachers%2C%20seats%2C%20and%20a%20stage%2C%20surrounded%20by%20litter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669427318893442a515675d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221342%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20shooter%20was%20perched%20on%20a%20rooftop%20some%20150%20yards%20from%20the%20stage%20at%20the%20campaign%20rally%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3EJabin%20Botsford%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20would-be%20assassin%20fired%20at%20least%20three%20rounds%20from%20a%20ro