5C%22%3ECrooks%20was%20seen%20crawling%20onto%20the%20roof%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20when%20the%20CS%20team%20saw%20and%20shot%20him%2C%20Pickle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20on%20how%20many%20anti-snipers%20to%20deploy%20may%20prove%20the%20most%20critical%20factor%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20made%20a%20decision%20that%20that%20number%20of%20counter-snipers%20was%20sufficient%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20obviously%2C%20in%20hindsight%2C%20they%20were%20wrong%20because%20there%20was%20a%20kid%20who%20was%20able%20to%20get%20up%20there%20on%20that%20rooftop%20and%20pull%20the%20trigger%20three%20times%20at%20least.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22978f4c2f-be40-4c47-b3b1-f0c87dcd0617%5C%22%3EHow%20many%20CS%20teams%20were%20deployed%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Law%20enforcement%20officers%20with%20snipers%20and%20helmets%20move%20around%20the%20stage%20at%20Trump's%20campaign%20rally%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669427cc5439fb59cebd3bf3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221370%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Secret%20Service%20has%20advance%20teams%20that%20scope%20out%20sites%20and%20make%20staffing%20recommendations%20ahead%20of%20major%20events%2C%20one%20expert%20said.%3Cp%3EJabin%20Botsford%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStaffing%20decisions%20would%20have%20been%20made%20at%20Secret%20Service%20headquarters%20in%20Washington%2C%20based%20on%20whatever%20agency%20personnel%20on%20the%20ground%20recommended%20after%20a%20several-day%20investigation%20of%20the%20site%2C%20Pickle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20advance%20team%20actually%20does%20a%20lengthy%20survey%2C%20where%20they%20look%20at%20everything%20and%20then%20recommend%20what%20they%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20they're%20stretched%20for%20resources%2C%20headquarters%20can%20say%20we%20can%20only%20get%20you%20one%20team%20out%20there.%20And%20that's%20not%20unusual%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20it%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Pickle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20always%20boils%20down%20to%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20it's%20not%20a%20resource%20problem%2C%20and%20the%20money%20was%20there%2C%20then%20it's%20still%20an%20allocation%20of%20resources%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20someone%20underestimated%20the%20manpower%20needed%20to%20keep%20Trump%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20how%20many%20snipers%20were%20present%2C%20the%20Secret%20Service%20would%20typically%20have%20%26quot%3B360-degree%20coverage%26quot%3B%20of%20an%20event%20where%20a%20sitting%20or%20former%20president%20is%20speaking%2C%20Cangelosi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20factors%20include%20the%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CS%20guys%20would%20probably%20say%20we%20were%20up%20there%20for%20four%20hours%20in%20100-degree%20heat%2C%20and%20if%20we%20had%20another%20team%20up%20here%20or%20drone%20support%20this%20wouldn't%20have%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Pickle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20may%20also%20have%20been%20focusing%20on%20a%20nearby%20tree%20line%2C%20seeing%20it%20as%20the%20primary%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20looking%20at%20everything%20that%20would%20hide%20a%20potential%20assassin%2C%26quot%3B%20Pickle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20assumption%20is%20that%20if%20I'm%20a%20bad%20guy%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20hide.%20Human%20nature%20is%20such%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20scanning%20the%20rooftops%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20empty%2C%20but%20then%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20focusing%20on%20that%20tree%20line%20because%20you%20think%20the%20bad%20guy%20is%20going%20to%20be%20hidden%2C%26quot%3B%20Pickle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20think%20the%20bad%20guy%20is%20going%20to%20be%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b2cd8aa-4441-40a9-a1c8-ec6e6b56a174%5C%22%3EInter-agency%20squabbles%20and%20intense%20public%20scrutiny%20are%20forthcoming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20would-be%20assassin%20opened%20fire%2C%20%26quot%3Beverything%20that%20happened%20up%20there%20was%20textbook%20and%20the%20way%20it%20should%20have%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Pickle%20said.%20The%20CS%20team%20returned%20fire%2C%20long-gun-toting%20counter-assault%20agents%20in%20black%20jumpsuits%20and%20helmets%20rushed%20the%20stage%2C%20and%20business-suited%20agents%20on%20the%20rally%20platform%20hurried%20Trump%20off%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20why%20wasn't%20he%20identified%20seconds%20sooner%3F%26quot%3B%20Pickle%20asked%20of%20the%20shooter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWas%20it%20caused%20by%20exhaustion%20from%20being%20on%20a%20100-degree%20roof%20for%20four%20hours%3F%20Was%20the%20CS%20team%20watching%20the%20heavy%20foliage%20there%2C%20which%20arguably%20was%20the%20best%20place%20to%20hide%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20open%20roof%20is%20not%20the%20best%20place%20to%20hide.%20If%20he%20climbed%20out%20onto%20an%20open%20rooftop%2C%20he%20was%20prepared%20to%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20worst%20nightmare%20for%20the%20Secret%20Service%20has%20always%20been%20a%20lone%20gunman%20who%20hasn't%20been%20announcing%20his%20views%20publicly%20and%20is%20ready%20to%20die.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPickle%20said%20Saturday's%20incident%20will%20be%20dissected%20for%20years%20to%20come%20and%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20in%20the%20training%20syllabus%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20circular%20firing%20squad%2C%26quot%3B%20Pickle%20predicted%20of%20the%20inter-agency%20finger-pointing%20and%20conspiracy%20theories%20that%20will%20play%20out%20a