0the%20museum's%20%26quot%3BLadies%20Lounge%26quot%3B%20exhibition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKirsha%20Kaechele%2C%20the%20museum's%20curator%2C%20previously%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fartanddesign%2F2024%2Fmar%2F20%2Fartist-behind-monas-ladies-only-lounge-absolutely-delighted-man-is-suing-for-gender-discrimination%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuardian%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20men's%20%26quot%3Bexperience%20of%20rejection%20is%20the%20artwork%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20delighted%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20case%20had%20gone%20to%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exhibition%20contained%20some%20of%20the%20museum's%20most%20notable%20artworks%2C%20including%20some%20said%20to%20have%20been%20produced%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpablo-picasso-heirs-sell-digital-art-pieces-artist-ceramic-work-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpanish%20Cubist%20Pablo%20Picasso%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20court%20ruled%20that%20the%20exhibition%20violated%20the%20state's%20Anti-Discrimination%20Act%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bpersons%20who%20do%20not%20identify%20as%20ladies%26quot%3B%20must%20be%20allowed%20entry%2C%20Kaechele%20made%20headlines%20after%20she%20moved%20several%20of%20the%20supposed%20Picassos%2C%20which%20had%20hung%20in%20the%20exhibition%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years%2C%20to%20a%20female%20toilet%20cubicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmona.net.au%2Fblog%2Fart-is-not-truth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20museum's%20website%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Kaechele%20said%20that%20the%20works%2C%20which%20included%20a%20copy%20of%20%26quot%3BLuncheon%20on%20the%20Grass%2C%20After%20Manet%2C%26quot%3B%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20been%20painted%20by%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20of%20a%20number%20of%20Picasso%20paintings%20I%20could%20borrow%20from%20friends%2C%20but%20none%20of%20them%20were%20green%20and%20I%20wished%20for%20the%20Lounge%20to%20be%20monochrome.%20I%20also%20had%20time%20working%20against%20me%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20cost%20of%20insuring%20a%20Picasso%E2%80%94exorbitant!%26quot%3B%20Kaechele%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20said%20she%20eventually%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20paintings%20with%20her%20%26quot%3Bown%20hands%20and%20the%20(perfectly%20shellacked)%20hands%20of%20my%20manicurist's%20niece%2C%20who%20is%20far%20more%20competent%20in%20pen%20and%20ink%20and%20thus%20assisted%20with%20the%20etching.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComments%20below%20the%20blog%20post%20show%20mixed%20reactions%2C%20with%20some%20labeling%20the%20stunt%20%26quot%3Bbrilliant%20and%20brave%26quot%3B%20while%20others%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20take%20people%20for%20fools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArt%20expert%20Christopher%20Heathcote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fculture%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fjul%2F13%2Fchildish-and-unprofessional-art-experts-say-monas-fake-picasso-stunt-may-undermine-gallerys-reputation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20thought%20%26quot%3Bthe%20entire%20episode%20is%20childish%2C%20unprofessional%2C%20and%20reflects%20poorly%20on%20Mona.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20being%20passed%20off%20as%20an%20art%20activist%20statement%20is%20the%20standard%20excuse%20used%20for%20attention-seeking%20sensationalism%2C%26quot%3B%20Heathcote%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20forgery%20prompted%20a%20reevaluation%20of%20other%20works%20displayed%20in%20the%20Ladies%20Lounge%2C%20and%20Kaechele%20revealed%20that%20some%20other%20items%20were%20also%20not%20genuine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaechele%20admitted%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bmink%20rug%26quot%3B%20supposedly%20made%20by%20%26quot%3BPrincess%20Mary's%20royal%20furrier%26quot%3B%20was%20actually%20made%20of%20low-grade%20polyester%2C%2