ation%20Centre%20(I4C)%20in%20a%20public%20advertisement.%20This%20could%20be%20a%20con%20that%20can%20make%20people%20%26quot%3Ba%20victim%20of%20cyber%20fraud%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20ad%20cautioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20I4C%20suggested%20counter-measures%20before%20clicking%20or%20responding%20to%20such%20emails%3A%20check%20if%20the%20email%20has%20originated%20from%20an%20authentic%20government%20website%20that%20ends%20with%20%26quot%3Bgov.in%26quot%3B%3B%20check%20the%20internet%20for%20information%20regarding%20officials%20named%20in%20the%20email%3B%20and%20call%20the%20mentioned%20department%20to%20verify%20the%20email%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20issued%20a%20public%20advisory%20alerting%20email%20users%20about%20fraudulent%20e-mails%20bearing%20names%2C%20signatures%2C%20stamps%2C%20and%20logos%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20Cyber%20Crime%20and%20Economic%20Offence%2C%20Central%20Economic%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20(CEIB)%2C%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20and%20Cyber%20Cell%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20letter%20attached%20to%20these%20emails%2C%20as%20per%20the%20advisory%20issued%20on%20July%204%2C%20made%20allegations%20of%20child%20pornography%2C%20pedophilia%2C%20cyber%20pornography%2C%20sexually%20explicit%20exhibits%2C%20etc.%20against%20the%20receivers%20of%20the%20said%20e-mails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fraudsters%2C%20it%20said%2C%20use%20different%20e-mail%20addresses%20for%20sending%20such%20fake%20e-mails%20with%20attachments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20receiver%20of%20any%20such%20email%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20this%20fraudulent%20attempt.%20It%20is%20informed%20to%20the%20general%20public%20that%20any%20such%20e-mails%20with%20the%20attachment%20should%20not%20be%20responded%20to%20and%20such%20cases%20may%20be%20reported%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station%2Fcyber%20police%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Cyber%20Crime%20Coordination%20Centre%20(I4C)%2C%20an%20organisation%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20to%20deal%20with%20cyber%20crimes%20in%20a%20comprehensive%20manner%2C%20had%20issued%20a%20similar%20advisory%20in%20August%20last%20year%20cautioning%20users%20against%20such%20counterfeit%20emails%20impersonating%20the%20name%20of%20its%20CEO%20bearing%20subject%20titles%20like%20'urgent%20notification'%20and%20'court%20notification'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20misleading%20emails%20are%20targeted%20to%20various%20government%20offices%2C%20and%20individuals%20and%20falsely%20accuse%20them%20of%20cyber%20crimes%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20respond%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20I4C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20logos%20of%20I4C%2C%20IB%2C%20and%20Delhi%20Police%20used%20in%20these%20emails%20are%20%26quot%3Bintentionally%20fake%2C%20deceptive%20and%20created%20with%20malicious%20motives%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20officers%20in%20the%20national%20capital's%20Central%20Secretariat%20received%20such%20suspicious%20emails%20last%20week%20which%20were%20falsely%20stated%20to%20have%20been%20issued%20by%20a%20person%20working%20at%20%26quot%3BMEA%20Messaging%20Team%20NIC%20High%20Commission%20of%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MHA%20and%20I4C%20ad%20issued%20on%20Sunday%20said%20such%20suspicious%20emails%20and%20other%20types%20of%20cyber%20frauds%20should%20be%20reported%20immediately%20to%20www.cybercrime.gov.in%20or%20call%20the%20cyber%20crime%20helpline%20no%201930.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720972020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F43at22o8_hacker-generic-cybercrime-generic-cyber-scam-generic_625x300_12_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fe-n