ire%20tournament%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20will%20oppose%20any%20hybrid%20model%20proposals%20during%20the%20ICC's%20annual%20conference%20in%20Colombo%20from%20July%2019-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB's%20unwavering%20position%20comes%20in%20response%20to%20Indian%20media%20reports%20claiming%20that%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India's%20(BCCI)%20reluctance%20to%20send%20the%20Indian%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20prestigious%20tournament%20scheduled%20between%20February%20and%20March%20next%20year.%20Given%20the%20strained%20political%20relations%20and%20security%20concerns%2C%20India%20have%20not%20toured%20Pakistan%20since%20the%202008%20Asia%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20has%20hinted%20at%20requesting%20the%20ICC%20to%20implement%20a%20hybrid%20model%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20allowing%20India%20to%20play%20their%20matches%20in%20a%20neutral%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cricketing%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20been%20fraught%20with%20political%20and%20security%20issues%20since%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20attacks%2C%20after%20which%20bilateral%20series%20were%20suspended.%20The%20last%20time%20India%20toured%20Pakistan%20was%20in%202008%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20The%20countries%20have%20since%20met%20only%20in%20ICC%20events%20or%20Asia%20Cup%20tournaments%20held%20in%20neutral%20venues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20impasse%20occurred%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%2C%20where%20the%20BCCI's%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20led%20to%20the%20adoption%20of%20a%20hybrid%20model.%20While%20this%20allowed%20the%20tournament%20to%20proceed%2C%20it%20resulted%20in%20Pakistan%20losing%20the%20hosting%20rights%20for%20the%20semi-final%20and%20final%20matches.%20This%20outcome%20has%20made%20the%20PCB%20even%20more%20determined%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20is%20held%20entirely%20on%20Pakistani%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20challenging%20position%2C%20tasked%20with%20balancing%20the%20interests%20of%20both%20cricketing%20powerhouses%20while%20maintaining%20the%20integrity%20of%20international%20competitions.%20The%20upcoming%20ICC%20Annual%20Conference%20in%20Colombo%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20critical%20juncture%20where%20the%20PCB%20will%20vehemently%20oppose%20any%20hybrid%20model%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720966500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdno889vo_india-pakistan_625x300_30_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpcbs-big-threat-if-team-india-refuses-to-travel-to-pakistan-for-champions-trophy-2025-report-6104100%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20taken%20a%20firm%20stance%20on%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20entirely%20within%20its%20territory%2C%20dismissing%20any%20considerations%20for%20a%20hybrid%20model.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpcbs-big-threat-if-team-india-refuses-to-travel-to-pakistan-for-champions-trophy-2025-report-6104100%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpcbs-big-threat-if-team-india-refuses-to-travel-to-pakistan-for-champions-trophy-2025-report-6104100%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpcbs-big-threat-if-team-india-refuses-to-travel-to-pakistan-for-champions-trophy-2025-report-6104100%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forest%20Whitaker%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Emperor%20of%20Ocean%20Park%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20Provocative%20Murder-Mystery%2C%20Once%20It%20Finds%20Its%20Footing%3A%20TV%20Review%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720966500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FEOOP_101_01645_R.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D56