08%2Fwhere-to-eat-in-kolkata-classics-best-heritage-eateries-map-anindya-basu-dolon-dutta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememories%20about%20Kolkata%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20he%20replied%20that%20the%20beauty%20of%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20still%20persists%20from%20his%20earlier%20visits%20to%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20kebabs%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20lies%20in%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%2C%20there%20is%20a%20bucketload%20of%20places%20in%20the%20city%20that%20also%20serve%20their%20own%20take%20on%20this%20iconic%20snack.%20For%20instance%2C%20Chaccha%20Jaan%20on%20Chowbhagha%20Road%2C%20which%20makes%20a%20mean%20%3Cem%3Erumali%20roti%20kebab%20roll%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20Kareem%E2%80%99s%3B%20Kusum%20Rolls%3B%20Campari%2C%20which%20is%20famous%20for%20the%20fish%20%3Cem%3Etandoori%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%3B%20and%20Zeesha%2C%20whose%20brain%20egg%20roll%20is%20a%20treat%20to%20the%20senses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20you%E2%80%99ll%20agree%20that%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20is%20its%20versatility%20%E2%80%94%20a%20quality%20that%20has%20helped%20it%20reach%20global%20stages.%20The%20filling%20can%20be%20altered%20to%20suit%20local%20palates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProof%20lies%20in%20a%20MasterChef%20Australia%20Season%2013%20episode%20in%202021%20where%20Indian-origin%20home%20chef%20Depinder%20Chhibber%20made%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Erolls%2C%20adding%20a%20twist%20to%20them%20by%20making%20the%20snack%20out%20of%20crayfish%20and%20deep%20lobster%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealong%20with%20egg%2C%20pickled%20onions%2C%20mint%2C%20coriander%20chutney%2C%20fresh%20carrots%2C%20capsicum%2C%20and%20coriander%20leaves.%20She%20served%20the%20rolls%20with%20mint%20and%20coriander%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20tomato%20%3Cem%3Ekasundi%