07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-3-1720617480-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356340%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsimran%20secured%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2016%20on%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20UPSC-IFS.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20a%20plan%20B%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20advise%20aspirants%20to%20spend%20years%20and%20years%20solely%20on%20exam%20preparation.%20This%20exam%20isn%E2%80%99t%20everything.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20diversify%20and%20not%20put%20all%20your%20eggs%20in%20one%20basket.%20That%20should%20be%20your%20initial%20approach.%20Many%20people%20waste%20years%20chasing%20glamour.%20Instead%2C%20dedicate%20two%20to%20three%20years%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20unable%20to%20clear%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20perfectly%20fine%20to%20explore%20other%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308203%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-upsc-cse-for-working-professionals-ias-divya-mittal-shares-tips-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlongside%20your%20job%2C%20you%20can%20prepare%20for%20this%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hard%20work%20never%20goes%20to%20waste%3B%20I%20can%20attest%20to%20this%20after%20almost%2010%20years%20of%20my%20journey%2C%20which%20fortunately%20culminated%20in%20success%20in%20this%20field%2C%