4%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356341%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsimran%20secured%20210%20marks%20out%20of%20300%20in%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20prepare%20effectively%2C%20I%20searched%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282477%2Fupsc-cse-syllabus-previous-years-question-paper-tips-ias-officer-anisha-shrivastav%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20question%20papers%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20This%20helped%20me%20understand%20UPSC%E2%80%99s%20expectations%20and%20gauge%20the%20adequacy%20of%20my%20preparation.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20mastering%20subjects%20that%20typically%20challenge%20other%20candidates%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20competitive%20edge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20an%20edge%20over%20his%20competitors%2C%20Harsimran%20stressed%20reverse%20engineering.%20%E2%80%9CI%20identified%20the%20most%20challenging%20questions%20from%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20diligently%20searched%20for%20relevant%20information%20online.%20Once%20I%20found%20the%20appropriate%20source%20books%2C%20I%20stuck%20to%20them%20to%20gain%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20the%20subjects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20strategy%2C%20he%20successfully%20cleared%20