0rice.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20teach%20you%20how%20to%20adjust%20for%20more%20rice%20or%20how%20to%20find%20out%20if%20something%20is%20cooked.%20When%20is%20the%20right%20time%20to%20add%20salt%3F%20This%20practical%20knowledge%20by%20first-hand%20experience%20was%20missing%20in%20cookbooks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1720615037.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Krish%20Ashok%20is%20the%20author%20of%20Masala%20Lab%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1720615037.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1720615037-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1720615037-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1720615037-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKrish-Ashok-2-1720615037-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356298%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKrish%20Ashok%20is%20the%20author%20of%20Masala%20Lab%3A%20The%20Science%20of%20Indian%20Cooking%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20on%20vacations%20back%20home%2C%20he%20started%20observing%20them%20and%20realised%20that%20this%20is%20all%20practical%20knowledge%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20theoretical.%20Since%20science%20could%20explain%20the%20hows%2C%20whats%20and%20whys%2C%20the%20author%20started%20writing%20about%20it%20on%20X.%20His%20food%20deconstruction%20posts%20and%20threads%20became%20widely%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20lived%20abroad%20for%20seven%2