0their%20innovative%20products%20aimed%20at%20a%20harmless%20resolution%20of%20such%20conflicts.%20The%20startup%20was%20also%20featured%20on%20a%20Shark%20Tank%20episode%20in%20season%203%2C%20bagging%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201.5%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInnovations%20that%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20animals%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ayan%20is%20a%20robotics%20engineer%20who%20worked%20on%20building%20consumer%20robots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20working%20in%20the%20city%20when%20a%20friend%20highlighted%20the%20issue%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F175235%2Fassam-wildlife-conservation-dulu-borah-elephant-man-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20human-wildlife%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fa%3EHe%20explained%20how%20this%20issue%20exists%20and%20has%20been%20resulting%20in%20losses%2C%20and%20I%20was%20quite%20taken%20aback%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20research%2C%20Ayan%20realised%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20how%20it%20is%20prevalent%20in%20most%20states%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20bid%20to%20protect%20their%20fields%2C%20farmers%20would%20resort%20to%20things%20like%20electric%20fencing%20which%20could%20potentially%20hurt%20the%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ayan%20wanted%20to%20help%20farmers%20suffering%20from%20wild-life-related%20losses.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-