20help%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20then%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20join%20the%20company%20and%20support%20his%20wife.%20Today%2C%20they%20supply%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351707%2Fdoon-gooseberry-farm-dehradun-sisters-amla-farming-growing-mangoes-brinjals-tomatoes-lemons-in-hilly-areas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowders%20and%20masalas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20over%20500%20families%20and%20are%20present%20in%2025%20organic%20shops%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20besides%20being%20available%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20even%20opened%20their%20own%20shop%20in%20Coimbatore%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20now%20sell%20over%20120%20kg%20of%20products%20every%20month%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20over%20Rs%2060%2C000%20monthly.%20Their%20powders%20today%20include%20sambhar%2C%20rasam%2C%20different%20spinach%20(keerai)%20powders%2C%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20podi%3C%2Fem%3E%20masalas%20like%20biryani%2C%20chicken%2C%20mutton%20and%20soup%20powders.%20Their%20bestsellers%20are%20the%20soup%20powders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20hopes%20that%20more%20women%20come%20forward%20to%20start%20their%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20this%20from%20our%20rented%20house%20with%20just%20Rs%202%2C000.%20You%20need%20to%20believe%20in%20yourself.%20There%20are%20many%20avenues%20to%20educate%20yourself%20and%20expand%20your%20horizons.%20The%20sky%E2%80%99s%20the%20limit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20buy%20the%20products%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finiyaorganics.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Sudha%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720448911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsudhaa-min-1720445265.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20a%20teacher%2C%20Sudha%20started%20experimenting%20with%20different%20podis%20and%20masalas%20to%20make%20her%20daughter's%20food%20tastier.%20The%20Coimbatore-based%20entrepreneur%20grew%20her%20experiment%20into%20a%20startup%20called%20Iniya%20Organics%2C%20which%20sells%20spices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355942%2Forganic-masala-spices-in-coimbatore-tamil-nadu-iniya-organics-business-podis-health-mixes%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2275%20Ponds%20%26amp%3B%20Counting%3A%20Started%20at%2017%2C%20This%20Man%20Is%20on%20a%20Mission%20To%20Revive%20Water%20Bodies%20in%20His%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20loves%20a%20revolutionary.%20But%20no%20one%20wants%20someone%20of%20their%20own%20to%20put%20their%20life%20on%20the%20line%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rambabu%20Tiwari%20deduced%20this%20early%20on%20in%20life.%20Thirteen%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Class%2012%20student%2C%20set%20out%20on%20a%20quest%20to%20tackle%20Bundelkhand%E2%80%99s%20water%20woes%2C%20he%20never%20assumed%20that%20this%20decision%20would%20shape%20the%20trajectory%20of%20his%20life%20and%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20did%20he%20expect%20his%20work%20to%20earn%20him%20a%20mention%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20radio%20programme%20%E2%80%98Mann%20Ki%20Baat%E2%80%99%20(27%20June%202021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%2030-year-old%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332504%2Fwater-heroes-in-india-revamp-lakes-rivers-canals-solve-drought%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20hero%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20moniker%20that%20he%20has%20been%20bestowed%20with%20by%20the%20villagers%20of%20Adhawan%20in%20Bundelkhand%20%E2%80%94%20emphasises%20that%20recognitions%20and%20accolades%20come%20secondary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20fuels%20his%20drive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20lies%20in%20the%20way%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20light%20up%20each%20monsoon%20as%20the%20rains%20grace%20his%20village%2C%20filling%20up%20the%20rural%20ponds%20that%20had%20lain%20barren%20for%20years.%20Watching%20them%20spring%20to%20life%20is%20all%20the%20validation%20he%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20achieving%20the%20feat%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20sometimes%20the%20stubborn%20climate%20posed%20hurdles%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20relentless%20heat%20waves%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20with%20temperatures%20touching%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20would%20cause%20the%20water%20bodies%20to%20run%20dry%20%E2%80%94%20while%20other%20times%2C%20it%20was%20his%20friends%20and%20family%20who%20were%20against%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tiwari%20has%20remained%20unfazed.%20And%20his%20stoicism%20was%20eventually%20met%20with%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20chat%20with%20him%2C%20we%20explore%20how%20this%20PhD%20student%E2%80%99s%20model%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296139%2Ftamil-nadu-man-quits-dubai-job-to-revive-water-bodies-help-lakhs-after-cyclone-india-water-warriors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviving%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20well%20be%20a%20gold%20standard%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%20that%20is%20struggling%20with%20water%20problems%20in%20the%20face%20of%20changing%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAs%20precious%20as%20gold%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nursery%20rhymes%20we%20grew%20up%20hearing%20are%20rooted%20in%20our%20memories.%20Likewise%20for%20Tiwari%20and%20the%20children%20of%20his%20village%3B%20albeit%20the%20rhymes%20were%20slightly%20different.%20Veering%20away%20from%20the%20popular%20ones%2C%20these%20verses%20emphasised%20the%20crucial%20importance%20of%20water%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDhaura%20tera%20paanee%20gajab%20kari%20jae%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Egagaree%20(matakee)%20na%20phootai%2C%20khasam%20(pati)%20maree%20jae.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETranslating%20these%20lines%2C%20and%20underscoring%20their%20meaning%2C%20Tiwari%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bthe%20rhyme%5D%20originated%20centuries%20ago%20when%20the%20women%20of%20the%20village%20would%20walk%20for%20miles%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20a%20certain%20pond.%20The%20water%20was%20considered%20so%20prized%20and%20expensive%20that%20the%20women%20would%20often%20pray%20to%20God%20to%20not%20let%20the%20%3Cem%3Ematkas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud%20pots)%20crack%20and%20tell%20Him%20that%20He%20could%20take%20away%20their%20husbands%20instead.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rhyme%2C%20though%20morbid%2C%20encapsulates%20the%20pedestal%20on%20which%20water%20was%20put%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rambabu%20Tiwari's%20pond%20revival%20projects%20are%20targeted%20at%20mobilising%20community%20efforts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355528%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERambabu%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20pond%20revival%20projects%20are%20targeted%20at%20mobilising%20community%20efforts%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%E2%80%99s%20earliest%20memories%20involve%20being%20scolded%20for%20accidentally%20breaking%20a%20pot%20or%20two%20while%20playing%20around%20the%20house%20with%20his%20friends.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20drop%20was%20considered%20to%20be%20gold%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20owes%20to%20the%20complex%20relationship%20that%20Bundelkhand%20has%20had%20with%20water.%20The%20region%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20once%20interspersed%20with%20thick%20forests%20%E2%80%94%20is%20now%20characteristic%20of%20bare%2C%20hilly%20terrain.%20And%20as%20a%20report%20by%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Disaster%20Management%20(2014)%20suggests%2C%20the%20droughts%20are%20to%20blame%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20concluded%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332290%2Fmaharashtra-water-scarcity-drought-prone-jalna-district-gets-aid-water-bodies-desilted%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esevere%20drought%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20sharply%20increased%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years%20in%20Bundelkhand.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20records%20from%20the%20Government%20show%20a%20spell%20of%20one%20drought%20in%2016%20years%20during%20the%2018th%20and%2019th%20centuries%20in%20Bundelkhand.%20From%201968%20to%201992%2C%20the%20region%20saw%20a%20drought%20every%20five%20years.%20However%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20the%20region%20has%20already%20suffered%20seven%20years%20of%20drought%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%20this%2C%20conserving%20water%20was%20second%20nature%20for%20Tiwari.%20But%20these%20ideals%20tended%20to%20get%20blurred%20when%20he%20moved%20to%20Allahabad%20for%20further%20studies%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bathroom%20of%20his%20own%3B%20showers%20for%20baths%3B%20unlimited%20water%20supply%20and%20no%20one%20having%20to%20walk%20miles%20to%20fetch%20it%2C%20introduced%20Tiwari%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20world.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20his%20luck.%20But%20while%20the%20initial%20weeks%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9Cfantasy%20life%E2%80%9D%20pushed%20all%20thoughts%20of%20water%20scarcity%20out%20of%20his%20mind%2C%20weekend%20visits%20back%20home%20did%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20forget%20about%20his%20village%E2%80%99s%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20to%20draw%20parallels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20that%20Rambabu%20Tiwari%20has%20helped%20revive%20was%20previously%20barren%20and%20filled%20with%20silt%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20that%20Rambabu%20Tiwari%20has%20helped%20revive%20was%20previously%20barren%20and%20filled%20with%20silt%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20having%20a%20shower%20bath%20one%20day%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20how%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F230520%2Fro-wastewater-use-reuse-safe-drink-plants-recycling-water-save-bathroom-flush-mumbai-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eamount%20of%20water%20I%20was%20consuming%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20equal%20(if%20not%20more)%20to%20the%20amount%20that%20my%20entire%20family%20would%20consume%20in%20a%20day.%20I%20thought%20of%20my%20mother%20back%20home%20who%20would%20walk%20for%20hours%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20evening%20to%20fetch%2020%20buckets%20of%20water%20for%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20needs.%20It%20did%20not%20feel%20right%20to%20waste%20water%20this%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20of%20environmental%20studies%2C%20Tiwari%20also%20felt%20a%20moral%20obligation%20to%20not%20let%20sustainable%20lessons%20be%20limited%20to%20a%20textbook%2C%20but%20instead%20to%20put%20them%20to%20practice.%20And%20that%20day%2C%20a%20man%20with%20a%20vision%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20initial%20efforts%20to%20rally%20against%20water%20wastage%20were%20met%20with%20taunts.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20a%20water%20issue%20in%20Bundelkahnd%2C%20go%20do%20something%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20told%20by%20his%20batchmates%20whom%20he%20appealed%20to%20opt%20for%20bucket%20baths%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20shower.%20Reluctant%20to%20give%20up%2C%20Tiwari%20continued%20to%20oppose%20the%20shower%20system%20in%20the%20hostel%2C%20and%20he%20notes%20how%2C%20in%20time%2C%20the%20water%20wastage%20was%20brought%20down%20significantly%20by%2040%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20battle%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20over.%20He%20then%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20his%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-2-1720083434.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20revival%20of%20ponds%20first%20involves%20cleaning%20the%20pond%20and%20collecting%20all%20debris%20that%20have%20accumulated%20in%20it%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-2-1720083434.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-2-1720083434-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-2-1720083434-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-2-1720083434-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-2-1720083434-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355532%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20revival%20of%20ponds%20first%20involves%20cleaning%20the%20pond%20and%20collecting%20all%20debris%20that%20has%20accumulated%20in%20it%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-3-1720083510.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiwari%20was%20joined%20by%20villagers%20who%20saw%20their%20efforts%20as%20a%20service%20to%20God%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-3-1720083510.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-3-1720083510-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-3-1720083510-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-3-1720083510-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-3-1720083510-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355534%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETiwari%20was%20joined%20by%20villagers%20who%20saw%20their%20efforts%20as%20a%20service%20to%20God%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20plan%20to%20change%20the%20landscape%20of%20Bundelkhand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConceiving%20change%20in%20a%20region%20that%20had%20almost%20succumbed%20to%20acute%20drought%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%20Tiwari%20points%20out.%20Moreover%2C%20because%20the%20villagers%20had%20lost%20hope.%20The%20young%20graduate%E2%80%99s%20plan%20was%20simple.%20He%20would%20return%20home%20every%20weekend%20from%20Allahabad%20where%20he%20was%20studying%2C%20and%20mobilise%20the%20people%20of%20his%20village%20to%20desilt%20the%20ponds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20observed%20that%20the%20ponds%20had%20a%20great%20capacity%2C%20but%20because%20they%20were%20choked%20with%20silt%2C%20their%20water%20accumulation%20capacity%20had%20gone%20down.%20So%2C%20even%20during%20the%20monsoons%2C%20the%20entire%20pond%20could%20not%20be%20filled.%20Come%20January%20every%20year%2C%20we%20faced%20water%20shortage%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20story%20of%20the%20first%20pond%20of%20focus%20%E2%80%98Bajrang%20Sagar%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20pond%20with%20an%2011%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20traditional%20unit%20to%20measure%20the%20area%20of%20a%20plot%20of%20land%3B%201%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3D%20%E2%85%93%20to%201%20acre)%20capacity%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20water%20bodies%20in%20the%20village%20and%20situated%20right%20near%20Hanuman%20Mandir.%20When%20I%20would%20call%20people%20to%20desilt%20the%20pond%20initially%2C%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20keep%20prayers%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandir%20%3C%2Fem%3E(temple)%20and%20people%20started%20coming%20in%20hordes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-4-1720083584.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Desilting%20the%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20took%20a%20total%20of%20eight%20weeks%20with%20the%20villagers%20putting%20in%2024%20hours%20of%20work%20each%20week%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-4-1720083584.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-4-1720083584-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-4-1720083584-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-4-1720083584-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-4-1720083584-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355537%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDesilting%20the%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20took%20a%20total%20of%20eight%20weeks%20with%20the%20villagers%20putting%20in%2024%20hours%20of%20work%20each%20week%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20and%20a%20few%20chosen%20friends%20began%20explaining%20the%20importance%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281458%2Fenvironment-activist-revives-water-bodies-lakes-coimbatore-water-warrior-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesilting%20the%20pond%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20devotees%20who%20had%20gathered.%20That%20day%2C%20before%20%3Cem%3Eprasada%3C%2Fem%3E%20(food%20and%20water%20offered%20to%20devotees)%20was%20distributed%2C%20the%20crowd%20pulled%20up%20their%20sleeves%20and%20began%20digging%20the%20silt%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20began%20seeing%20the%20job%20as%20manual%20labour%20that%20they%20were%20offering%20to%20God%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20time%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20began%20coming%20for%20this%20weekly%20effort.%20It%20took%20eight%20weeks%2C%20with%20us%20digging%20for%2024%20hours%20every%20Monday%2C%20for%20the%20pond%20to%20be%20completely%20cleared.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20points%20out%20that%20there%20was%20no%20compulsion%20or%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20of%202015%20was%20phenomenal%20for%20the%20village%20of%20Adhawan%20which%20stood%20stunned%20as%20the%20pond%20filled%20up%20to%20its%2011%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecapacity.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20quantity%20was%20so%20much%20that%20farmers%20could%20even%20use%20it%20for%20their%20irrigation%20needs%2C%20aside%20from%20people%20using%20the%20water%20for%20their%20home%20and%20personal%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-5-1720083725.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pond%20that%20Tiwari%20and%20the%20villagers%20of%20Adhawan%20dug%20spanned%2011%20bighas%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-5-1720083725.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-5-1720083725-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-5-1720083725-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-5-1720083725-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-5-1720083725-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355541%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20pond%20that%20Tiwari%20and%20the%20villagers%20of%20Adhawan%20dug%20spanned%2011%20bighas%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20the%20case%20of%20any%20village%2C%20Adhawan%20was%20witnessing%20migration.%20People%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20see%20a%20reason%20to%20live%20in%20a%20drought-prone%20region%20anymore%2C%20Tiwari%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CFour%20to%20five%20families%20had%20moved%20from%20the%20village%20and%20found%20jobs%20as%20security%20guards%20and%20drivers%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Pune.%20But%20when%20they%20heard%20about%20the%20success%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F199310%2Fmumbai-man-revives-traditional-ponds-vasai-virar-water-hero-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20pond%20revival%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20started%20making%20plans%20to%20return%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismantling%20social%20constructs%20was%20exciting%20for%20Tiwari%20and%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20crux%20on%20which%20their%20water%20project%20had%20been%20founded%20was%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EGaav%20ka%20paani%20gaav%20mein%2C%20khet%20ka%20paani%20khet%20mein%20%3C%2Fem%3E(The%20water%20of%20the%20village%20should%20remain%20in%20the%20village%2C%20and%20the%20water%20of%20the%20fields%20should%20be%20restricted%20to%20the%20fields.)%20To%20ensure%20this%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20desilting%20many%20ponds%20around%20Bundelkhand%20across%20the%20villages%20of%20Marka%2C%20Pindaran%2C%20Gahbra%2C%20Jhalokhar%2C%20Mohnipur%20among%20others.%20We%20also%20started%20building%20troughs%20of%20two%20feet%20height%20around%20every%20field%20so%20that%20the%20rainwater%20could%20collect%20in%20this%20and%20be%20used%20for%20farming%20purposes%20even%20after%20the%20monsoons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Foa--noZyZ1g%3Fsi%3DPCal_G3LmdeNRJu6%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20and%20his%20team%20also%20organised%3Cem%3E%20paani%20chaupals%3C%2Fem%3E%20(water%20awareness%20sessions)%20where%20they%20challenged%20the%20villagers%20to%20question%20their%20water%20usage%2C%20and%20water-saving%20techniques.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20conducted%20over%20300%20of%20these%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20started%20making%20water%20friends%20who%20we%20call%20%E2%80%98jal%20mitras%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%20Sharing%20more%20about%20this%20concept%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20work%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20respective%20villages%2C%20research%20water%20bodies%20and%20their%20capacities%2C%20work%20with%20tank%20management%20committees%20to%20see%20which%20ponds%20can%20be%20revived%20a